										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In recent years, we certainly haven&#8217;t seen a shortage of major changes to keywords and matching behavior from Google Ads. From the introduction of close variants to the deprecation of modified broad match, updates to query matching logic, and more, the future of keywords in Google Ads will likely continue to ebb and flow. Today, I&#8217;m going to help you navigate these types of updates and share expert advice on how to prepare for the future of Google Ads keywords.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#google-ads-keyword-trends">6 things to know about Google Ads keywords in 2025</a></li>
</ul>
